PRODUCTION SHALITA
GRANT 'S DEPARTURE Section::::Production .
Section::::Shalita Grant 's departure .
It was announced on January 31 , 2018 , that Shalita Grant who plays NCIS agent Sonja Percy would be departing the series after the nineteenth episode of the season .
According to Grant and CBS , this decision is " mutual " and " amicable . "
